title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

com.android.alarm.permission.SET_ALARM.description: Allows the application to set an alarm in an installed alarm clock application. Some alarm clock applications may not implement this feature.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.MANAGE_DOCUMENTS.description: Allows an application to manage access to documents, usually as part of a document picker.

co.app.makemyplate.permission.C2D_MESSAG.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

During this weekly cheat meal, you can eat whatever you want. This will help keep your motivation strong the rest of the week, reduce cravings, and prevent binging. So you can safely cheat once a week without seeing ill effects on your waistline.

Taste it. Savor it. Eat guiltlessly, but not mindlessly!"

playstore_details.title: MakeMyPlate Diet Meal Planner
playstore_details.description:
Your diet app is now a no brainer with Make My Plate, the visual diet meal planner. Choose your complete meal plan to meet your diet goals,  and we'll be your personal diet assistant for an healthy eating. We automatically present you with thousands of diet meals including your favorite foods when eat out, an automatic grocery list, and community support to keep you motivated.


Features 

• 3 FREE Visual diet meal plans that meet your needs, created by top RD's & nutritionists, including recipes.
• No more portion size guessing, using our visual plate portion control system you get to eat the exact portions of your meal.
•   All meals are balanced and contain complete nutritional info including nutrients, macros, and calorie calculations.
•   Combine your favorite eat out food chain or genre within your diet meal plan using our eat out meal planner, including approved by RD's eat out meals on menu.
•   An automatic grocery list that is created from your meal plan and can be configured manually.
•   Get a realtime support and professional guidance you need from our 24/7 live community chat that is managed by a professional nutritionist.
•   Don't like our suggestions? Easily swap them out or replace one of the dishes within your meal to only eat foods you like.
•   Set your reminders and motivational tips to keep you on track and build new healthy habits.

Premium features 

Professional PRO diet meal plans to choose from including:
•  The low carb diet Plan also known as the popular Ultimate NY Diet.
•  The Red Carpet Diet, also known as The Celebrity Diet.
•  A complete Vegan meal plan.
•  The ultra Gluten Free & celiac meal plan.
•  The ultimate Paleo diet meal plan.

Food diaries & calorie counters are out. Take the guessing out of what is good for your nutrition targets and meal plan a head to reach your weight goals. Using our visual diet meal planner, there's no more guessing. All you have to do is stick to your plan, we've got you covered.

Our free diet meal plans give our users a complete solution to manage their weight throughout calorie restriction and offer all features above. As a premium user we provide the MakeMyPlate total experience for special diet needs of users who seek to boost their health, weight loss journey or maintain specific diet guidelines.

Try out our free meal plans to see if the MakeMyPlate new way of diet appeals to you, and upgrade to a PRO meal plan when you're ready to boost up your diet goals.

Privacy policy: http://www.makemyplate.co/private_policy.html
Terms of use: http://www.makemyplate.co/terms.html
